  <text>
     <body>
     <div type="poem">
   <pb facs="2"/>
   <p>
      <figure>
         <figDesc>depiction of a besom or bunch of twigs, a stick or staff, and some rope or string, all separate</figDesc>
      </figure>
   </p>
   <lg>
      <l>Thre thinges to be noted </l>
      <l>all in their kynde,</l>
      <l>A staff, a beesom, and </l>
      <l>with, that wyll wynde.</l>
   </lg>
   <lg>
      <l>¶ A beesome of byrche, for babes verye fyt,</l>
      <l>A longe lastinge iybbet for loubbers as meete,</l>
      <l>A wyth to wynde vp, that these wyll not keepe,</l>
      <l>Bynde all vp in one, and vse it to sweepe.</l>
   </lg>
   <p>
      <figure>
         <figDesc>depiction of a broom, composed of a besom or bunch of twigs, a stick or staff, and some rope or string, bound together</figDesc>
      </figure>
   </p>
</div>
